1)build:
make

2)clean:
make clean

3)usage:
a.add_nalu_head_info
It will add extra 16 byte header of indicating nalu size.
/add_nalu_head_info input.es output_16byte_header.es

b.del_nalu_head_info
It will delete extra 16 byte header before nalu.
/del_nalu_head_info input.es output_remove_16byte_header.es

c.es_mess
It will flip random bit of random byte.
h264:
./es_mess -c h264 -i input.h264 -o output_mess.h264

h265:
./es_mess -c h265 -i input.h265 -o output_mess.h265
